sequenceDiagram
    participant GH as GitHub Action
    participant S as Source (iana.org)
    participant Sec as Security (Trivy)
    participant R as Registry (ghcr.io/opensource-distroless)
    
    GH->>S: curl tzdata202x.tar.gz
    S-->>GH: Download pristine source
    
    GH->>GH: Execute `make install` to unpack profiles
    
    GH->>Sec: Trivy SCA/SBOM scan on directory
    Sec-->>GH: output: tzdata-sbom.spdx.json
    
    GH->>R: Push intermediate scratch container (artifacts-tzdata)
    GH->>R: Sign via Cosign OIDC credentials
